# This chart symlinks library charts into charts/. Some of those libs contain a
# test harness in a test-chart/ dir whose own charts/ symlinks back into the
# lib, so we have to ignore these dirs here to break the symlink loop Helm's
# loader would otherwise hit while walking the chart directory: the symlink
# points back into a directory that contains that chart (whose charts/ symlinks
# back again), so the walk would never terminate. It's a filesystem traversal
# loop, not a dependency-graph cycle.
#
# One alternative would be `repository: file://...` dependencies in Chart.yaml,
# but because helm-janitor doesn't run `helm dependency build` that isn't an
# option.
test-chart/
